{"tid":591053,"cid":11,"subCid":0,"title":"《悍戰太平洋2》景甜重戲份","createTime":"2018-03-13T08:00:48.000Z","updateTime":"2018-03-13T10:20:37.000Z","uid":38671,"like":2,"dislike":18,"uniUserReply":14,"replies":[{"pid":"3b0dcb12531383ff0071e3083a8d6c8d696f6d2c","tid":591053,"uid":38671,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-03-13T08:00:48.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n <img src=\"https://static.appledaily.hk/images/e-paper/20180311/large/1520762360_88fd.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fstatic.appledaily.hk%2Fimages%2Fe-paper%2F20180311%2Flarge%2F1520762360_88fd.jpg&h=04516dfe&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n荷李活電影《悍戰太平洋2：起義時空》（Pacific Rim：Uprising）年前分別到中國及澳洲取景，歷籌備5年後終在本月上映。《悍戰太平洋2》加入不少亞洲面孔，包括張晉、趙雅芝兒子黃愷傑及千葉真一兒子新田真劍佑，而近年活躍荷李活嘅強國女星景甜更會戲份頗重，連上集女主角菊地凜子都成為陪襯。<br />\n<br />\n《悍戰太平洋2》由炮製劇集《夜魔俠》（Daredevil）嘅Steven S. DeKnight執導，講述於首集嘅十年後日本，怪獸踩入鬧市摧毀，主角換上《星球大戰》（Star Wars）系列男星約翰保也加（John Boyega），而奇連伊士活（Clint Eastwood）兒子史葛伊士活（Scott Eastwood）都拍住上抗敵，而景甜飾演嘅邵立雯（Liwen Shao）亦係重要角色，佢係個擁有高智商但性格冷漠嘅女強人，為抵禦怪獸威脅，景甜一手創立邵氏工業，又與主角們並肩作戰。片中景甜有幾場用英語唇槍舌戰嘅戲份，上年被指拖跨《長城》以及《金剛：骷髏島》（Kong：Skull Island）後，唔知今次能否挽回面子。"},{"pid":"d4a2166e6a9a88f01d264901f1d37cc3c3fe1128","tid":591053,"uid":18569,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-03-13T08:15:49.000Z","msg":"呢套野一定變到好似天煞地球反擊戰差唔多<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"5b41e485bdd27b1cd29ba035d1d9ac71f48f24f2","tid":591053,"uid":30006,"like":5,"dislike":2,"score":3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-03-13T08:17:41.000Z","msg":"Feel到好雷下呢套野"},{"pid":"1083b4fac77b41779d69e8b4745c35ed3223552b","tid":591053,"uid":32675,"like":5,"dislike":0,"score":5,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-03-13T08:24:45.000Z","msg":"本身見啲機甲同變型金剛一樣輕漂漂已經反胃,仲有哩個柒頭係度喎<br />\n入場?不了"},{"pid":"c8e9bafe2d7fadc7ee7f25335a73142b8c78957f","tid":591053,"uid":171788,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-03-13T08:39:55.000Z","msg":"留名 飲蒙牛 或 招牌被打爛"},{"pid":"9f297f13ec84aad7647ed88a5ada5ee5e18b7bc5","tid":591053,"uid":33553,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-03-13T08:48:29.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/23.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 我要睇架妹唔係大陸妹啊<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/23.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"c5a2f2700595c21bdc0dccee2152cd7162f1e510","tid":591053,"uid":66202,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-03-13T08:57:28.000Z","msg":"換左導演<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n機械人似變形金剛<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n再加個景甜<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n咁嘅牌面...<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"4dc12e0597768db29a4065c4b769c5f3cfd05e06","tid":591053,"uid":16092,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-03-13T08:57:38.000Z","msg":"邵氏<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/shocking.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/shocking.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/shocking.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"7e2387823a10ee93e4b986801d4a369f4bad9137","tid":591053,"uid":110002,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-03-13T08:57:54.000Z","msg":"睇錯重甜戲份<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"aa10401d16ebff78ba80c6b958dddf187c9b7f9b","tid":591053,"uid":88999,"like":6,"dislike":0,"score":6,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-03-13T08:59:52.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=1vU7XqToZso\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.youtube.com%2Fwatch%3Fv%3D1vU7XqToZso&d=RRFyPJExOFzaatkg3WeVHywN645TRhVPBLeqKBQ2Igw%3D&h=b27d54a6\" target=\"_blank\">https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=1vU7XqToZso</a><br />\n<br />\n無呢首做背景音樂唔撚睇<br />\nBT都廢事"},{"pid":"80810870ea609363fd416049dbf217d0558de372","tid":591053,"uid":118120,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-03-13T09:00:22.000Z","msg":"上集真係有世界末日, 靠機甲拯救世界feel<br />\n今集變左軍事學園, 一班後生MK軍官好威威渣機械人打怪物"},{"pid":"d1c66ac36ff49e6a793769945480c3797258fb09","tid":591053,"uid":70629,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-03-13T09:02:55.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://hk.news.appledaily.com/local/daily/article/20071111/10405017\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.news.appledaily.com%2Flocal%2Fdaily%2Farticle%2F20071111%2F10405017&d=RRFyPJExOFzaatkg3WeVHywN645TRhVPBLeqKBQ2Igw%3D&h=40b7d4ea\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.news.appledaily.com%2Flocal%2Fdaily%2Farticle%2F20071111%2F10405017&h=1a431065\" target=\"_blank\">https://hk.news.appledaily.com/local/daily/article/20071111/10405017</a><br />\n<br />\n【本報訊】《蝙蝠俠──黑夜之神》（ The Dark Knight）在港拍攝接近尾聲，原來這套國際大製作，除了會有香港夜景和擔演路人甲乙丙的港人外，藝人陳冠希更是唯一有份參與的本港藝人。在片中只屬「串星」的他昨與著名演員摩根費曼（ Morgan Freeman）演對手戲，據知陳冠希在戲中飾演秘密警察，屬一名「無間道」，表面上是協助蝙蝠俠等人的正派人物，實質是一名內奸；他的出現，令人得以窺探該電影的一小部份劇情。<br />\n<br />\n現年27歲的陳冠希能操流利英語，去年踏足荷李活主演西片《咒怨2》（ The Grudge2）。據知今次是由他所簽的美國經理人公司 William Morris，向《蝙蝠俠》製作公司推薦演出，雖然是演奸角，戲份只有一天，但因此片為大製作，故他一口答應。<br />\n陳在劇中演繹一名秘密警察，專責在港接待基斯頓比爾（ Christian Bale）飾演的榮布斯（即蝙蝠俠）和摩根費曼飾演的霍路斯（蝙蝠俠的武器專家），協助兩人套取情報，但他實為內奸。片中陳冠希接待摩根費曼的秘密基地，就是中環中心。<br />\n<br />\n又令我諗起呢單新聞 , 當年都話陳冠希個角色好重要 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/slick.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"d1ee623890344c407a6ce6bb5608b76a3927b3fc","tid":591053,"uid":56729,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-03-13T09:09:24.000Z","msg":"得啦唔洗睇喇 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/z.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"9146a4bbe57f7dd21008ac985875c28c9176bd6a","tid":591053,"uid":23635,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-03-13T10:20:37.000Z","msg":"同期好似有Ready player one，我睇佢好過睇景甜啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}